To reproduce our results, no installation is needed since we provide a virtual machine image.

First download the VM, the location of the VM can be found in VM_LOCATION file in this repository.
Then, simply double-click on RAICC.ova, it will trigger virtualbox into importing.
After the importation is done, simply run the VM and floow the instructions of README file.

Please follow the step described in Oracle website to import the virtual machine:
  - https://docs.oracle.com/cd/E26217_01/E26796/html/qs-import-vm.html

If for some reason, one does not want to use our virtual machine, follow the instructions available at:
    - https://github.com/lilicoding/soot-infoflow-android-iccta/wiki/Detailed-description-of-IccTA-usage
    - https://github.com/lilicoding/soot-infoflow-android-iccta/wiki/Configuration%E2%80%93free-usage-of-IccTA
